<head>COMMONER</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">老百姓</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>HUMAN of less than NOBLE status.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. Pǐ fū 匹夫 (ant. jūn zǐ 君子 "gentleman; freeman") and the rarer xì rén 細人 is a purely sociological term referring to a person without public office.</p>
<p>2. Xiǎo rén 小人 (ant. jūn zǐ 君子 ) is a term of moral or personal appraisal and refers to a person of minor worth or of no moral merit.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
